# Sessions Grid Row - Prerequisite Hover Feature
# Fixes ilios/ilios#5512

## Changes to Component (sessions-grid-row.js)

Add this getter to the component class:

```javascript
// Getter for prerequisite session titles
get prerequisiteTitles() {
  const prerequisites = this.args.session?.prerequisites || [];
  if (prerequisites.length === 0) {
    return null;
  }
  
  const titles = prerequisites.map(prereq => prereq.title).filter(Boolean);
  return titles.length > 0 ? titles.join(', ') : null;
}
```

## Changes to Template (sessions-grid-row.hbs)

Add the title attribute to display prerequisites on hover:

```handlebars
<div class="sessions-grid-row" title={{this.prerequisiteTitles}}>
  {{! ... rest of template ... }}
</div>
```

Or if there's a specific element for the session title:

```handlebars
<span class="session-title" title={{this.prerequisiteTitles}}>
  {{@session.title}}
</span>
```

